
For information about building NCAR Graphics from source, please see
the "NCAR Graphics UNIX Installer's Guide" that you should have received
with your copy of NCAR Graphics.  You should also read the "NCAR
Graphics Release Notes" before doing anything else.

Full documentation for NCAR Graphics can be found via the URL:

	http://ngwww.ucar.edu/

Documentation is also available in PostScript format.  Please check with
your system administrator as he/she should have received it with the 
rest of the NCAR Graphics distribution.



